      "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/32/3/16/17",
      "text": [
        "١٦. وَقَالَ (عليه ‏السلام): تَذِلُّ الْأُمُورُ لِلْمَقَادِيرِ حَتَّى يَكُونَ الْحَتْفُ فِي التَّدْبِيرِ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.sayed-ali-raza": [
          "16. Amīr al-mu’minīn, peace be upon him, said: All matters are subject to destiny, so much so that sometimes death results from effort."
        ]
      }
    }
